Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been stolen!\NA picture more valuable than my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Saint Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:01:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely get some evidence\Non you today, Saint Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh! Not the painting that I stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the painting "Evening Primrose",\Nstolen from the city museum last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. It's... oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also a missing painting,\Nstolen two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! What is this all about?!\NShall we hear your explanation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She appeared again last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she did, she did!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This time it was a mansion in Ward 16.\NMeimi, did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking as if\Na strange ghost appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Saint Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Her ponytail flutters in the wind\Nas she steals only from the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of her classy figure\Npeople call her Saint Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one knows her true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Her tactful capers\Nhave never failed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's as lightfooted as the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And just what's so\Nwonderful about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail or Sacred Tail,\Nwhichever it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A thief is a thief!\NHow sickening, to call her "wonderful".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bet you'd like to meet her, too,\NAsuka, Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Saint Tail is a mature lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't even look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! A pest like her!\NThis is what she looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what kind\Nof person Saint Tail is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These are her crimes for\Njust the past month...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven jewel robberies and\Ntwo stolen paintings, ten thefts total.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My suspicion is that it's all\Nbecause of Saint Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd... I don't remember\Ntaking any jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, Detective Asuka keeps\Nslipping up again and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we believe\Nanything his son says?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump me in with my father!\NI'll be the one who catches Saint Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail wouldn't be so cool\Nif somebody like you could catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop me Siera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haneoka, Mr. Asuka!\NThe two of you just stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:05:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister-in-training Seira.\NColdhearted Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Coldhearted is much too cruel.\NIt is all the teachings of our Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You passed a girl on your way in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Saori.\NShe came to ask God for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a young girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Her grandfather is a jewelry appraiser.\NOne day, he was brought two sapphires.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them was the "Blue Meteorite",\Na very unique and expensive gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As a precaution against theft\Nthe owners had made a fake duplicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the duplicate was so well made,\Nthat the gems got mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't tell which\Nwas the real "Blue Meteorite".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the dealer, Umido,\Nasked her grandfather for the appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How does God\Nfit into a situation like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem.\NNow the grandfather is asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taken in by the gem's beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He lied to Umido, telling him that\Nthe fake gem was the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he bought the other gem,\Nthe real one, at a cheap price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fraud. He's a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But a good human being regrets what\Nhe's done and tries to correct it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, we're going to be\Nof assistance with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking it was real, Umido sold the\Nfake "Blue Meteorite" to a rich woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think we should go\Nabout making things right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:07:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think switching the real gem\Nthat Saori's grandfather has...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with the fake gem that was sold\Nshould do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The real gem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for you to make\Nyour appearance, Saint Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner will be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that! It's my new magic trick!\NBeautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, you've got the hands of a wizard.\NI love it! The next show will be a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you are making\Na mess of the room again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it? Meimi, you're\Ngoing to take after me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who decided that? Meimi's going to take\Nafter her mother, aren't you Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be joking!\NYour previous occupation was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that took\None look at me and fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to get to work.\NI've got to help people in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be where\Nshe keeps the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange... why is it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been stolen!\NThe "Blue Meteorite"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Better get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We steal back the gems that we sell\Nand then resell them to another sucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no rules in making money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi... you can't! It's dangerous.\NAnd I don't have information on Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, nothing's impossible\Nfor St. Tail! I'll get through somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's check out\Nthe houses of the wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then overlap that with the locations\Nof unsolved crimes for the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So her next victim is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail!\NI won't let you get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The alarm went off,\Nso we came over to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened, Mr. Kaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, a kid got himself caught\Nin our alarm system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At this hour? Who's the little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Asuka's son, is it?\NWell, how rude of me. Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, son, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail is coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past month, this is the only place\Nthat hasn't been hit by a theft. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't catch Saint Tail,\Nso I'm doing it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got other things to do\Nthan chase Saint Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to meet this Saint Tail, myself.\NI hear she's a great thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Saint Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't turn on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just exchange the fake\None for the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what this was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how ingenious you are.\NStealing back the gems that you sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you call me a thief!\NWhat evidence do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The evidence are these jewels,\NMr. Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all the jewels that\Nwere stolen in the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She always has a\Nvalid reason for her capers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail is not a crook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaido, the real crook is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be rattling on for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail, you're not\Ngetting away either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!\NDon't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail, don't be a coward!\NCome down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Challenge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At least send me a warning\Nthe next time you plan to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a bit fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't these all the stolen jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail... She seems to be\Nabout the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I touched her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I present this award of appreciation\Nfor the good deed you've performed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one request, would you help us\Nin the arrest of Saint Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an official\Ninvestigation badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing this will get\Nyou in anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We definitely want to utilize your\Nexpertise and knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Saint Tail case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, with the cooperation\Nof the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Saori came to church\Nto express her thanks to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They returned the jewel to its owner.\NI guess that's the end of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!\NBye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you got an award.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! And next time,\NI'm gonna get that Saint Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway...\Nhang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Just watch me.
